PCP
[[File:PCP_happy.jpg|thumb|PCP makes you happy!]]

[[Image:Show him who's boss.jpg|thumb|right|The way to solve all your problems]]

Phencyclidine (a.k.a. PCP / angel dust / lovely / [[wut|hog]] / Sherman Hemsley / loveboat / rocket fuel / illy) is often regarded as the most fucked up drug ever conceived. Even the most bad ass of stoners and druggies fear it due to the psychedelic effects of smoking said substance.  Some of the most [[SA|awful]] and disgusting things have been done under the influence of PCP, such as trying to hack your own legs off, eating a white chick's lungs (unsurprisingly it was done by a black person), the creation of most of the pages on [[ED]] and biting out a [[lol wut|four year old's eye]].

==What is PCP?==

Do you feel depressed, lonely, and generally suffer malaise and/or a low self esteem? Then you should try PCP. PCP is made of cyanide and pure win, as well as different adulterant chemicals depending on the maker. Some of the side effects of PCP may include but are not limited to; decreased inhibitions, chronic amnesia, homicidal paranoia, spontaneous suicide, megalomania, and cannibalism. In doses low enough to show no brain activity none of these may occur, but take any more than a pinch and you'll be Arnold Schwarzenegger in Terminator II moments afterward.

==The Effects of PCP==

[[Image:PCP and its effects.jpg|thumb|right|Those spiders were high]]

PCP is particularly known for the crazy things people do while under the influence of it.  These include, but are not limited to, trying to commit suicide, [http://forums.officer.com/forums/showpost.php?p=700031&postcount=22 ejaculating on policemen], [http://forums.officer.com/forums/showpost.php?p=692548&postcount=10 ripping your balls off], jumping out of buildings (and not dying), fucking your family, ripping your face off and feeding it to dogs, and gouging your eyes out.  There are many reported cases of wacky things done under the influence of PCP, and these are the more notable ones.

According to the [[weev|local ED druggie]], the sensations of taking PCP include euphoria, intense body high, an increase in energy, as well as a dreamlike state with intense closed-eye visuals.

===Big Lurch===

Perhaps the most famous of the PCP related murders, Big Lurch (Antron Singleton) was an [[bad|up-and-coming]] black person.  Under the influence of PCP he murdered his roommate [[Azn|Tynisha Ysais]], and then went Thanksgiving Dinner on her chest, carving it with a knife and then [[wut|eating her lungs]].  After this he ran around naked before being captured.

He tried to plead insanity, but the judge decided that eating someone was too heinous a crime to be excused, and therefore sentenced him to a lifetime of [[rape|cell sharing]] with [[Bubba]].

Also he had an album released while on trial.  At least he got something done.

[[Image:PCP_addict.jpg|thumb|left|This is what will happen to anyone who uses PCP more than once.]]

===Faceless Man===

Now if you thought the last on was bad enough, then [[Bill Nye|consider the following]]. You may question why there is a faceless man on the left. Well apparently this man had to prove his badassery of taking PCP by doing some thing that not even the [[FTM|manliest of man]] would dare to do. After taking PCP, he asked himself the following; “[[I DUNNO LOL|what if I rip off my own face]]”?  He proceeded to do so by using parts of a broken mirror. However, that was just not enough for him. No, he fed the remains of his face to his dog. Supposedly, these dogs had their stomachs pumped to recover the partially digested bits of face. To reconstruct the man's face (if you can call it that) plastic surgery was attempted.

[[Death|No one knows what happened to the man]].

(for further reading consult [http://www.snopes.com/horrors/drugs/facepeel.asp this])

===Angelo Mendoza===

A (Mexican) man named Angelo Mendoza Senior was taking a PCP trip when his four year old son started to annoy him.  Doing what any good father would do, he lashed out at Angelo Mendoza Junior and ate his left eye, while mutilating his other.  He then left his apartment in a wheelchair whilst trying to chop his legs off with an axe.

Perhaps one of the highlights of the whole incident was what the four year old said to authorities when they arrived at his house:

{{quote|My daddy ate my eyes out}}

[[Image:Houston'seye.jpg|thumb|right|Eye+(pcp+fork)=ruined career]]

===Houston===

[[Rap|R & B]] singer Houston was high on PCP after a show when he finally gave up on life.   Saying he was going up to his room to read the Bible, he tried to commit suicide by jumping out a window but was promptly talked out of it by his entourage.  He then decided stab out his eye [[wat|with a fork]].

He is currently trying to get his music career back and has a glass eye.

